==Standard dialogue==
=== During Making Friends with My Arm===
{{main|Transcript:Making Friends with My Arm}}

===After Making Friends with My Arm===
* '''Wolfbone:''' How are things at Weiss?
* '''Player:''' Snowflake and My Arm are ruling the town together, and now I've built them a special fire, they can grow goutweed there.
* '''Wolfbone:''' So My Arm taught Weiss the farming knowledge of the Stronghold trolls. Now Stronghold trolls can be given firemaking knowledge from Weiss, like I promised.
* '''Player:''' Snowflake gave me a book containing all the information she could find from Odd Mushroom's notes.
* '''Wolfbone:''' Give it to Burntmeat. He can teach trolls what they want to know from it.
* {{tcond|If the player does not have the [[Weiss fire notes]]:}}
** '''Player:''' Hopefully Snowflake will give me another one.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has a copy of the Weiss fire notes:}}
** '''Player:''' Now that My Arm has taught the Weiss trolls what he knows about farming, here's a book containing what the Weiss trolls know about firemaking.
** '''Wolfbone:''' Odd Mushroom invented lots of clever stuff with Snowflake. Might be handy for Stronghold trolls.
** '''Burntmeat:''' Let Burntmeat see...
** {{tbox|pic=Weiss fire notes detail.png|The troll looks at the scientific notes.}}
** '''Burntmeat:''' Uh...
** {{tbox|pic=Weiss fire notes detail.png|The troll wrinkles his forehead in thought.}}
** '''Burntmeat:''' Yeah, lotsa learnings here. Very clever stuff. We oughta reward you.
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|Don't give me more burnt meat.}}
*** '''Player:''' Don't give me more burnt meat. I've been here before, and you gave me a load of burnt meat.
*** '''Burntmeat:''' Silly human pretends he don't like Burntmeat's lovely burnt meat! But okay, Burntmeat will not make any more for you. Ever.
*** '''Player:''' Ever? You're never ever going to give me burnt meat again?
*** '''Burntmeat:''' No more burnt meat from Burntmeat, ever. Wolfbone here has made reward for you instead.
*** '''Wolfbone:''' Yes, I have learnt a lot here from my friend Burntmeat, and he has let me prepare a reward for you myself.
*** {{tbox|pic= Weiss fire notes detail.png|pic2=Burnt meat detail.png|As you no longer wish to receive burnt meat from Burntmeat, Wolfbone presents you with a reward instead.}}
*** {{tact|receives=a full inventory of [[burnt meat]]}}
*** {{tbox|pic= Weiss fire notes detail.png|You hear a suspicious munching sound from the direction of Burntmeat.}}
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|That's very kind of you.}}
*** '''Player:''' That's very kind of you.
*** '''Burntmeat:''' Burntmeat got feeling you no like Burntmeat's burnt meat. Burntmeat made some for you before, an' you not seem grateful. So Burntmeat will not make any more for you. Ever.
*** '''Player:''' Ever? You're never ever going to give me burnt meat again?
*** {{tact|above}}

===After quest and after delivering fire notes===
* '''Burntmeat:''' Ah, you come back again.
* '''Wolfbone:''' How are things at Weiss?
* '''Player:''' Snowflake and My Arm are ruling the town together, and now I've built them a special fire, they can grow goutweed there.
* '''Wolfbone:''' I plan to stay here, in the Stronghold, with my friend Burntmeat, but it good to hear of my home. Thank you.
* '''Burntmeat:''' Stronghold trolls not all that interested in firemaking, after all, but t'anks for bringing book anyway. It taste lovely.
* '''Player:''' ... you're welcome.
* {{tact|end}}
